                  Students who are working full time are not eligible for the Education and Training Scheme.
                </div>

                <div class="form-group pt-flow--student pt-showIfEngagedInFullTimeEmployment">
                  <label class="uikit-text-input__label display-inline" for="relationshipToStudent" id="">The veteran is my</label>
                  <select class="uikit-text-input input-auto display-inline" name="relationshipToStudent" id="relationshipToStudent" type="text"
